           Responsive & Adaptive UI


Responsive : same UI in many sizes for one platform
Adaptive : Different UI for each platform




          Responsive & Adaptive Tools

1- MediaQuery Widget
2- LayOutBuilder Widget

======================================

* expanded
* flexible
* fitted Box
* Aspect Ratio
* Constraints or intrinsic widgets


======================================

           Responsive Text ( fontSize )
1- scale factor for each platform (mobile , tablet , desktop)
2- each scale factor has min,max default size

* scale factor = width / chosen breakpoint for each platform
  - chosen breakpoint for mobile = 400
  - chosen breakpoint for tablet = 700
  - chosen breakpoint for desktop = 1000

* responsive font size = base font size * scale factor

// important Note

// the sizedBoxes are used to add space between widgets in responsive layout
// has not responsive height & width
// and also padding and margin are not responsive